    "Strauss et al. (2018) conduct a survey on choice-based revenue management.",
    "They focus on the design and estimation of discrete choice models for revenue management and on the dynamic availability control problem under customer choice behaviour, which contains an assortment optimization problem.",
    "Hence, the authors provide a brief overview of related literature on assortment optimization, which is structured according to the underlying choice models.",
    "In contrast, Qi et al. (2020) review literature on data-driven research in retail operations with a particular focus on studies in three core aspects of retail operations, namely assortment optimization, order fulfillment, and inventory management.",
    "The section on assortment optimization starts with an introduction to parametric choice models and their estimation, followed by the description of selected literature on assortment optimization under parametric choice models."
